parse.title: List of people on the United States cover of Rolling Stone (2010s)

text.*:
This is a list of people (real or fictional) appearing on the cover of Rolling Stone magazine in the 2010s. This list is for the regular biweekly issues of the magazine, including variant covers, and does not include special issues. Issue numbers that include a slash (XXX/YYY) are combined double issues.

  • 2 2011
  • 3 2012
  • 4 2013

  • 6 2015
